<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16559</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我好了！” 凯蒂喊道，“我和以前一样了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16560</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19893</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拉里帮凯蒂上了干草车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24224</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他抓住乔伊的手，也把她拉了上去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24225</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>佛格森叔叔是拉里的爸爸，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26861</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29458</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他坐在拖拉机的前面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33506</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“阿杰，大家都上来了吗？” 他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33507</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿杰看了看坐在干草堆上的朋友们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38290</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41826</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他抬头看了看他的大姐艾米丽。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41827</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她笑着点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44398</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48594</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“都上来了，佛格森叔叔。” 阿杰喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48595</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54694</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>佛格森叔叔启动了拖拉机的发动机，干草车出发了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54695</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“祝你生日快乐。” 劳拉唱道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿杰用双手捂住了脸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69715</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“祝你生日快乐。” 大家一起唱了起来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69716</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79508</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“祝你生日快乐，阿杰，祝你生日快乐！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79509</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84199</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们都鼓掌，欢呼起来！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84200</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90027</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你几岁了？” 凯蒂问，“四岁？五岁？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90028</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿杰跳了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95871</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我六岁了，你知道的！” 他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95872</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂笑着向他眨了一下眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104693</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>曼尼把手伸到劳拉的后面，用稻草挠她脖子的痒痒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104694</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110339</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！” 劳拉喊道，“有东西爬到我身上来了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110340</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一只毛茸茸的大蜘蛛！” 卢克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119193</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>劳拉尖叫起来。“快帮我拿掉它！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119194</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123663</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它太大了。” 卢克说，“不敢碰它。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123664</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有蜘蛛。” 乔伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130187</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“卢克，别开玩笑了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧！” 卢克说，“这个车上没有蜘蛛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139779</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我希望也没有黑蛇！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139780</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利维亚打了一下卢克的胳膊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是一条非常大的黑蛇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147459</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它甚至想要咬我来着！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147460</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152063</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说的和我听说的不太一样呢！” 拉里说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152064</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155300</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我听说的是你差点儿把它吓死了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155301</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159132</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家又都笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159133</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162846</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是很糟糕的一天。” 乔伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162847</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165154</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“先是我的帮手受伤了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，核桃价格又下降了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我以为我永远不能实现我的目标了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172837</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那后来呢？” 阿杰问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176729</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180364</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我就继续捡核桃呗！” 乔伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180365</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不过，凯蒂和奥利维亚给卢克、拉里、劳拉和卡洛斯打了电话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188004</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们在星期天早上都过来帮我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191588</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195128</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也去了。” 曼尼说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195129</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对！你也来了。” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203806</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家一起捡， 很快就把手推车装满了。” 奥利维亚说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203807</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“多诺万叔叔和乔伊每次都会把装满的手推车送到核桃收购站去。” 劳拉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211930</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215688</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们把手推车装满了三次。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215689</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219489</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我超额完成了目标。” 乔伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219490</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225643</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我挣了111.5美元！朋友们，谢谢你们！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的小提琴修好了吗？” 阿杰问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232487</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在店里呢。” 乔伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232488</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它很快就会变得和新的一样了哦！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239963</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就像我的脚踝一样！” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239964</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245756</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>干草车沿路颠簸着，佛格森叔叔开始唱歌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245757</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248963</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老丹·塔克是大人物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248964</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252516</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他用煎锅洗了脸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255128</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们也跟着唱了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255129</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊假装拉着小提琴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257841</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261020</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>用马车轮梳了头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261021</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他因牙痛痛死了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266496</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们唱着歌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266497</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270024</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>佛格森叔叔把车开进了树林。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274324</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们还没走多远，卡洛斯就发现了什么东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274325</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277725</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好像是篝火！” 他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277726</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“确实是篝火！” 劳拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是阿杰的爸爸。” 凯蒂喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285247</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们终于到了。” 莫根叔叔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288590</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291671</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他是阿杰和艾米丽的爸爸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291672</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我以为我得自己烤完所有的热狗呢！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295004</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们从干草车上跳了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304354</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“欢迎你们来参加阿杰的生日篝火会！” 艾米丽说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308383</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁想喝热苹果汁？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308384</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“阿杰得许一个生日愿望！” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318931</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不能把生日愿望告诉你。” 阿杰说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318932</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>322634</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不然，它就实现不了了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>322635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325870</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊对着阿杰笑了笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>325871</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>328151</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你也可以说别的愿望。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>80</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>328152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>332034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不用非得是你的生日愿望。” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>81</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>332035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336240</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那你就能告诉我们了！” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>82</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>336241</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>338728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好。” 阿杰说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>83</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>338729</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>344254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望明年能在柳树溪搞一个最大的 ‘坐干草车’ 活动！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>84</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>344255</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>349350</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我会邀请所有人的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>